    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A solid, no-nonsense ride for the practical buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives dependably, making it a great choice for everyday commuting and errands. The exterior shows some noticeable wear and scratches consistent with its age, and the interior reflects normal use over time. If you're looking for reliable transportation without the premium price tag, this could be the perfect fit for you!",
